# Straight trunk, fronds droop from crown down into upper part of lower cube.

# --- TRUNK (Y=0, center, sy=0,1) ---
S 0 0 0  1 0 1  Log
S 0 0 0  1 1 1  Log

# --- DROOPING FROND TIPS (Y=0, sy=2, cardinal) ---
S 0 0 0  0 2 1  Leaf
S 0 0 0  2 2 1  Leaf
S 0 0 0  1 2 0  Leaf
S 0 0 0  1 2 2  Leaf

# --- CROWN (Y=1, sy=0, center) ---
S 0 1 0  1 0 1  Log

# --- HORIZONTAL FRONDS (Y=1, sy=0, cardinal) ---
S 0 1 0  0 0 1  Leaf
S 0 1 0  2 0 1  Leaf
S 0 1 0  1 0 0  Leaf
S 0 1 0  1 0 2  Leaf

# --- CROWN TUFT (Y=1, sy=1, center) ---
S 0 1 0  1 1 1  Leaf
